Harms of too much freedom
　People tend to think that more [freedom] is a good thing.
　The threat of a new corona caused a rapid shift to telecommuting.
　　This is "more freedom."
　　Observation that it is not likely to have only positive effects
　　Rapid change is a source of stress.
　　The routines that had been formed are destroyed.
　　　lose one's rhythm

仮説
　Create new "constraints" for yourself that reduce your freedom.
　This may increase productivity.
